body:
A course designed specifically for people who want to feel confident about money and finance. Finance Fitness is for those who want to find their around a complex world. 

Topics include: 
What is going on in the Economy; 
Finance and Economic 
Terms and Concepts; 
Financial decisions for different life stages;
Saving and budgeting;
Investment options & Risks (bonds, equities, property, cash etc)
Managing debt and mortgages
